                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Barlow</persName>, United States
                        marshal, to Mr. <persName type="to">Fishy</persName> Secretary of
                        State.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">New York</hi>
                    </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1869-05-07">
                        <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 7, 1869</date>.</dateline>
                <p rend="flushleft">Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">Hamilton Fish</hi>, <hi rend="italic"
                        >Secretary of State:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Telegram just received. I will at once inquire.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FRANCIS C. BARLOW,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">United States Marshal.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
